item.description:
To edit the uplink transfor for your Thing Type, select your Thing Type and click the pencil button.
Insert the following JavaScript code into the Uplink Transform section:
var variables = payload.toString('ascii').split(&quot;,&quot;); var tmpFloat = parseFloat(variables[1]); var humFloat = parseFloat(variables[2]); return { payload: payload.toString('utf-8'), text: variables[0], humidity: humFloat, temperature: tmpFloat, timestamp: + new Date() };
